<p class="text-gold-100 text-xl lg:pt-48 pt-16"><span class="font-bold">TACO</span> presents</p>
<h1 class="mt-2 text-6xl">the 6th Annual <span class="font-cursive text-7xl text-gold-400">No Show Gala</span></h1>

<div class="lg:pr-48 font-light">
  <p class="text-xl mt-8">Join us for a night of not attending while supporting San Diego’s award-winning non-profit organization.</p>

  <p class="text-xl mt-8">Don’t get dressed up, don’t get a sitter, don’t pay for parking.</p>

  <p class="text-xl mt-8">Don’t do anything while supporting TACO’s work of feeding and caring for our unhoused friends and neighbors.
</div>

<div class="mt-8 w-fit lg:flex">
  <%= link_to products_path, class: 'text-black' do %>
    <div class="bg-gold-600 p-4 w-fit rounded">
      <div class="bg-gold-100 w-fit px-9 py-3 rounded border-4 border-black">
        <span class="text-4xl font-bold">R.S.V.P.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <p class="mb-16 pl-4 flex mt-4 self-center text-3xl font-light">by Oct 27, 2023</p>
</div>

<hr class="my-8 border-t border-gray-900">

<div class="mt-8 w-fit text-center inline">
  <h2 class="mt-14 text-4xl font-cursive">Guest list</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-light">See who else won't be there.</p>
  <div id="name-input-area">
    <%= link_to products_path, class: 'text-black' do %>
      <button id="add-name-button" class="mt-4 bg-green-200 text-black font-bold py-1 px-8 rounded">Add my name</button>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "guests/guest_list" %>
</div>
